        "date": "22 November",
        "description": "On 22 November, another Drag Night awaits you at Termix 🤩 On stage you’ll see TiFanny BiGest and Miss Chief, bringing a show full of energy, humor, and bold performances. If you’re in the mood for an evening that breaks out of the ordinary, this is your best choice. ✨",
