        "title": "New Year’s Eve Party",
        "date": "31 December",
        "description": "We’ll end 2025 together in the place we love most — on the dance floor of Club Termix! Come with friends, meet new faces, and celebrate the arrival of 2026 in style! 🥳 More information about presale on our Facebook.",
