        "title": "Kinky Techno Rave",
        "date": "6 February",
        "description": "Join us for the Kinky Techno Rave — a Berlin-inspired night of creativity, fetish and pure expression 🔥 Latex, leather, lace, pup, dom/sub… KINKY dress code is required 😈 Expect hard techno, a dark vibe, respect, consent and a truly safe space for all 🌑✨ No phones — just rhythm, energy and your real self 🖤 DJs KOBØV & PAUL KRIST will take over the night 🎧",
        "img_filename": "kinkyTechno",
